Amazon Web Service is an extension to Amazon that supplies on-demand cloud computing platforms. It can help your business in multiple ways that you can imagine. AWS offers numerous services, allowing you to launch, scale and grow your business in any industry, be it a start-up or a big organization.

As of 2021, AWS offers around 200 products and services that involve computing, storage, database, analytics, networking, development, management tools and more. It follows the structure of pay-as-you-go, where you only pay for the services, you have availed.

